Revision history for Solaris-SMF

1.0.1     2015-01-25 23:50:00+00:00 Europe/Dublin

 - Updated date format in this changelog.
 - Removed RELEASE_TESTING logic from module and tests.
 - Replaced Data::Dumper and debug statements with Log::Any and trace logging.
 - Replaced several sets of tests with @TestingMania Dzil group.

1.0.0     2015-01-24 17:24:18+00:00 Europe/Dublin

 - Released as 1.0.0.
 - Tested against Solaris 11 and Perls 5.16.3, 5.18.4, 5.20.1 and 5.21.8.

0.05    2015-01-24

 - Converted distribution to use Dist::Zilla.
 - Updated tests to skip rather than fail on non-Solaris systems.

0.04	2010-01-24

 - Services may now be enabled and disabled, provided you are running as a user with appropriate privileges.

0.03_01	2009-12-07

 - Added 'maintenance' state to the tests.

0.03	2009-12-02

 - Radically revised - it now does what it says on the tin! Unnecessary dependencies removed as well.

0.02	2009-12-01

 - Updated prerequisites to add 'Readonly' support.

0.01	2009-11-28

 - First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

